obj_root_law_sections_16_content:
  string
  line `(1) The Lalit Kala Akadami (Taking Over of Management) Ordinance, 1997`
  line `(Ord. 10 of 1997) is hereby repealed.`
  line
  line `(2) Notwithstanding the repeal of the Lalit Kala Akadami (Taking Over of Management) Ordinance,`
  line `1997 (Ord. 10 of 1997), anything done or any action taken under the said Ordinance shall be deemed to`
  line `have been done or taken under the corresponding provisions of this Act.`
